      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 34 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 34 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：壯于趾，征凶，有孚。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows its subject manifesting his strength in his toes. But advance will lead to evil,--most certainly.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
