      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 34 六五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 34 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：喪羊于易，无悔。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, shows one who loses his ram(-like strength) in the ease of his position. (But) there will be no occasion for repentance.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-034-da-zhuang__alignment-007">
